Introduction

CSVC is a four-member project girl group. The group was formed independently by CHEEZE's Dalchong (now using her former group's name CHEEZE as her stage name), Stella Jang, Lovey, and Park Moonchi. Their music is distributed by POCLANOS. They debuted on August 6, 2019, with the retro 1990s-themed digital single "Summer Love...".
